messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Remove phone number +12453344098 from my contact
I can remove that contact for you—could you let me know the contact’s name or person ID associated with the phone number +1 245 334 4098?
I don't have that info, just the number.

I can remove it for you, but I’ll need to know which contact record(s) to delete. If you’re not sure of the name or person ID, would you like me to remove every contact that has the phone number +1 245 334 4098, in case there are multiple?
Yeah, just delete any contact with that number.

I’m afraid I need the person ID(s) (or at least the names) of the contact entries to delete them—right now I can only remove contacts when I have that identifier.  
Could you please provide the person ID(s) or tell me the name(s) associated with the phone number +1 245 334 4098?
I don't have any other details, sorry. Could you figure out another way to remove it?

I’m sorry, but the only way I can actually delete a contact is if you provide the contact’s person ID (or at least the name) so I can target the right record. Could you open your contact list, locate the entry with the phone number +1 245 334 4098, and tell me the person ID (or the name) that appears with it? Once I have that identifier, I’ll remove it right away.
